  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Model-level commissioning event for a detergent DPP (no serial -- model-based per EU 2026/405).",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries GS1 product master data plus product-level detergent",
    "classification (detergentCategory, productForm); these describe the GTIN itself. No ilmd",
    "is used because the EPC is a bare GTIN (no lot qualifier) and we have no lot-specific data.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,eudet=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/detergent/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
